snippet.title: Diana and crying Baby Born dolls behind the door
snippet.description:
Diana Pretend Play with Baby Born Dolls. Kids toys suddenly appear outside the door. Diana starts playing with dolls and cares about them, like their mom. Then she cook yummy food for toys!
